ser to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":". Keep this property set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views."}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Note"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value tha